title: 204 - Immortal Killer Joggers
description:
MATERIAL: 100% Cotton

FIT: Relaxed.

DESIGN: The Immortal killer joggers are a fashion statement. With their loose-fitting design and unique puff printed graphic on both legs, these joggers are a striking visual piece. Inspired by our best-selling immortal joggers, these pants offer the same eye-catching style.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.
